    "In step one, we evaluated the measurement model by assessing the internal consistency and convergent and discriminant validities.",
    "Since the data from the previous step were acceptable, we applied the structural model to verify our hypothesis in step two.",
    "The possibility of multi-collinearity and common method bias (CMB) were checked before the data analysis was started.",
    "For the purpose of assessing multi-collinearity, we used the \"variance inflation factor -VIF\".",
    "Each VIF value must be < 3."
